data.description:
Welcome to this beautifully updated home in the quiet neighborhood of Azalea Ridge. This 4 bedroom 2.5 bathroom home features both an Open Livingroom and a flex room. You'll find thoughtful updates throughout the home including, SOLAR PANELS, installed May 2021 (30 year warranty), newer LAMINATE wood and tile flooring, fresh NEUTURAL PAINT & more! The beautiful, open kitchen has new flooring, a large island and huge walk-in pantry. The large Primary Suite includes a large walk-in closet, and double sinks in the bathroom with a large garden tub. The large fenced-in backyard is perfect for relaxing or entertaining guests. The community boasts TWO swimming pools, community center, playground & more! MUST SEE!
**See private remarks for solar panel info.*
Seller offering No Cost Appraisal and 1-0 interest buy down with preferred lender.
